result.name: Lucky Dessert

reviews.text: So much to taste, so little stomach 😆
Staff are mean and the portion of sweet soup is small.

New menu, same below average dessert. Too watery and sweet, lacking any flavour. Pancakes not made fresh therefore it becomes too soft and soaked in moisture. No quality at all at what used to be a very decent dessert place. And overpriced as well.
Good mix of Asian and fusion favourite desserts. Parking is a pain and now getting very pricey.
This is the original shop, with good quality.

result.name: 發記甜品

reviews.text:
很久沒有來這裡，見無需等候，便即內進就坐。

看看餐牌後，終明白是為甚麼，吃特式甜品可比吃頓普通晚飯來得昂貴。

最終只揀選了只售26元的金粟紫米露，不太甜，只是粟子的嚼感和紫米不太一樣。

後會有期……
甜品難食，價錢又高，無下次
還不錯吃，位置不多，而且糖水這邊也沒什麼好選擇
似是用粉開的芝麻糊，無芝麻香，失望。
So much to taste, so little stomach 😆
